{{Quote|Keira and Hayley had the coloring and the look we needed for the tight-knit family. And they take direction well, which is the most important thing.|[[Robin Gurland]], Episode II Casting Director|<ref name="Casting">{{SWArchive|url=episode-ii/bts/production/news20000822.html|text=Casting Update: Son of Local Talent}}</ref>}}
'''Keira Jane Wingate''' is an Australian former child actress who played [[Ryoo Naberrie]] in [[Star Wars: Episode III Revenge of the Sith|''Star Wars'': Episode III ''Revenge of the Sith'']]. She also filmed a scene as Ryoo Naberrie in [[Star Wars: Episode II Attack of the Clones|''Star Wars'': Episode II ''Attack of the Clones'']], though it was eventually cut from the final release. It can be found in the "Deleted Scenes" section of the [[Star Wars home video releases#Star Wars Episode II: Attack of the Clones|''Attack of the Clones'' DVDs]].

Wingate also appeared in the [[2001]] film [[Wikipedia:Lantana (film)|''Lantana'']] as Hannah Daniels, and in the [[2004]] TV movie [[Wikipedia:The Mystery of Natalie Wood|''The Mystery of Natalie Wood'']] as a very young [[Wikipedia:Natalie Wood|Natalie Wood]].

